var book = {
	"name": "Galatians",
	"numChapters": 6,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, an apostle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29059A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29059A\"></sup>—sent not from men nor by a man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29059B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29059B\"></sup> but by Jesus Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29059C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29059C\"></sup> and God the Father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29059D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29059D\"></sup> who raised him from the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29059E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29059E\"></sup>—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and all the brothers and sisters with me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29060F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29060F\"></sup>To the churches in Galatia:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29060G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29060G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Grace and peace to you from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29061H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29061H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>who gave himself for our sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29062I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29062I\"></sup> to rescue us from the present evil age,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29062J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29062J\"></sup> according to the will of our God and Father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29062K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29062K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>to whom be glory for ever and ever. Amen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29063L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29063L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I am astonished that you are so quickly deserting the one who called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29064M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29064M\"></sup> you to live in the grace of Christ and are turning to a different gospel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29064N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29064N\"></sup>—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>which is really no gospel at all. Evidently some people are throwing you into confusion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29065O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29065O\"></sup> and are trying to pervert<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29065P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29065P\"></sup> the gospel of Christ.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But even if we or an angel from heaven should preach a gospel other than the one we preached to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29066Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29066Q\"></sup> let them be under God’s curse!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29066R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29066R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As we have already said, so now I say again: If anybody is preaching to you a gospel other than what you accepted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29067S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29067S\"></sup> let them be under God’s curse!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Am I now trying to win the approval of human beings, or of God? Or am I trying to please people?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29068T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29068T\"></sup> If I were still trying to please people, I would not be a servant of Christ.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I want you to know, brothers and sisters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29069U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29069U\"></sup> that the gospel I preached<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29069V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29069V\"></sup> is not of human origin.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I did not receive it from any man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29070W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29070W\"></sup> nor was I taught it; rather, I received it by revelation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29070X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29070X\"></sup> from Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29070Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29070Y\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For you have heard of my previous way of life in Judaism,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29071Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29071Z\"></sup> how intensely I persecuted the church of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29071AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29071AA\"></sup> and tried to destroy it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29071AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29071AB\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I was advancing in Judaism beyond many of my own age among my people and was extremely zealous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29072AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29072AC\"></sup> for the traditions of my fathers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29072AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29072AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But when God, who set me apart from my mother’s womb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29073AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29073AE\"></sup> and called me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29073AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29073AF\"></sup> by his grace, was pleased",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>to reveal his Son in me so that I might preach him among the Gentiles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29074AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29074AG\"></sup> my immediate response was not to consult any human being.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29074AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29074AH\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I did not go up to Jerusalem to see those who were apostles before I was, but I went into Arabia. Later I returned to Damascus.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29075AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29075AI\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then after three years,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29076AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29076AJ\"></sup> I went up to Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29076AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29076AK\"></sup> to get acquainted with Cephas and stayed with him fifteen days.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I saw none of the other apostles—only James,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29077AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29077AL\"></sup> the Lord’s brother.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I assure you before God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29078AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29078AM\"></sup> that what I am writing you is no lie.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29078AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29078AN\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then I went to Syria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29079AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29079AO\"></sup> and Cilicia.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29079AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29079AP\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I was personally unknown to the churches of Judea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29080AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29080AQ\"></sup> that are in Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29080AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29080AR\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They only heard the report: “The man who formerly persecuted us is now preaching the faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29081AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29081AS\"></sup> he once tried to destroy.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29081AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29081AT\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And they praised God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29082AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29082AU\"></sup> because of me."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Then after fourteen years, I went up again to Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29083A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29083A\"></sup> this time with Barnabas.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29083B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29083B\"></sup> I took Titus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29083C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29083C\"></sup> along also.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I went in response to a revelation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29084D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29084D\"></sup> and, meeting privately with those esteemed as leaders, I presented to them the gospel that I preach among the Gentiles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29084E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29084E\"></sup> I wanted to be sure I was not running and had not been running my race<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29084F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29084F\"></sup> in vain.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Yet not even Titus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29085G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29085G\"></sup> who was with me, was compelled to be circumcised, even though he was a Greek.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29085H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29085H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This matter arose because some false believers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29086I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29086I\"></sup> had infiltrated our ranks to spy on<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29086J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29086J\"></sup> the freedom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29086K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29086K\"></sup> we have in Christ Jesus and to make us slaves.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>We did not give in to them for a moment, so that the truth of the gospel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29087L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29087L\"></sup> might be preserved for you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>As for those who were held in high esteem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29088M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29088M\"></sup>—whatever they were makes no difference to me; God does not show favoritism<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29088N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29088N\"></sup>—they added nothing to my message.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29088O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29088O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>On the contrary, they recognized that I had been entrusted with the task<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29089P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29089P\"></sup> of preaching the gospel to the uncircumcised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29089Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29089Q\"></sup> just as Peter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29089R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29089R\"></sup> had been to the circumcised.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For God, who was at work in Peter as an apostle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29090S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29090S\"></sup> to the circumcised, was also at work in me as an apostle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29090T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29090T\"></sup> to the Gentiles.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>James,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29091U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29091U\"></sup> Cephas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29091V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29091V\"></sup> and John, those esteemed as pillars,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29091W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29091W\"></sup> gave me and Barnabas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29091X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29091X\"></sup> the right hand of fellowship when they recognized the grace given to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29091Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29091Y\"></sup> They agreed that we should go to the Gentiles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29091Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29091Z\"></sup> and they to the circumcised.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>All they asked was that we should continue to remember the poor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29092AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29092AA\"></sup> the very thing I had been eager to do all along.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When Cephas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29093AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29093AB\"></sup> came to Antioch,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29093AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29093AC\"></sup> I opposed him to his face, because he stood condemned.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For before certain men came from James,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29094AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29094AD\"></sup> he used to eat with the Gentiles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29094AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29094AE\"></sup> But when they arrived, he began to draw back and separate himself from the Gentiles because he was afraid of those who belonged to the circumcision group.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29094AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29094AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The other Jews joined him in his hypocrisy, so that by their hypocrisy even Barnabas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29095AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29095AG\"></sup> was led astray.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When I saw that they were not acting in line with the truth of the gospel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29096AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29096AH\"></sup> I said to Cephas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29096AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29096AI\"></sup> in front of them all, “You are a Jew, yet you live like a Gentile and not like a Jew.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29096AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29096AJ\"></sup> How is it, then, that you force Gentiles to follow Jewish customs?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29096AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29096AK\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“We who are Jews by birth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29097AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29097AL\"></sup> and not sinful Gentiles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29097AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29097AM\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>know that a person is not justified by the works of the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29098AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29098AN\"></sup> but by faith in Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29098AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29098AO\"></sup> So we, too, have put our faith in Christ Jesus that we may be justified by faith in Christ and not by the works of the law, because by the works of the law no one will be justified.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29098AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29098AP\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“But if, in seeking to be justified in Christ, we Jews find ourselves also among the sinners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29099AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29099AQ\"></sup> doesn’t that mean that Christ promotes sin? Absolutely not!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29099AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29099AR\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If I rebuild what I destroyed, then I really would be a lawbreaker.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“For through the law I died to the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29101AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29101AS\"></sup> so that I might live for God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29101AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29101AT\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I have been crucified with Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29102AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29102AU\"></sup> and I no longer live, but Christ lives in me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29102AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29102AV\"></sup> The life I now live in the body, I live by faith in the Son of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29102AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29102AW\"></sup> who loved me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29102AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29102AX\"></sup> and gave himself for me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29102AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29102AY\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I do not set aside the grace of God, for if righteousness could be gained through the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29103AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29103AZ\"></sup> Christ died for nothing!”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>You foolish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29104A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29104A\"></sup> Galatians!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29104B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29104B\"></sup> Who has bewitched you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29104C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29104C\"></sup> Before your very eyes Jesus Christ was clearly portrayed as crucified.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29104D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29104D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I would like to learn just one thing from you: Did you receive the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29105E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29105E\"></sup> by the works of the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29105F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29105F\"></sup> or by believing what you heard?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29105G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29105G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Are you so foolish? After beginning by means of the Spirit, are you now trying to finish by means of the flesh?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Have you experienced so much in vain—if it really was in vain?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So again I ask, does God give you his Spirit and work miracles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29108H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29108H\"></sup> among you by the works of the law, or by your believing what you heard?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29108I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29108I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So also Abraham “believed God, and it was credited to him as righteousness.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29109J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29109J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Understand, then, that those who have faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29110K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29110K\"></sup> are children of Abraham.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29110L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29110L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Scripture foresaw that God would justify the Gentiles by faith, and announced the gospel in advance to Abraham: “All nations will be blessed through you.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29111M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29111M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So those who rely on faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29112N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29112N\"></sup> are blessed along with Abraham, the man of faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29112O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29112O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For all who rely on the works of the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29113P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29113P\"></sup> are under a curse,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29113Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29113Q\"></sup> as it is written: “Cursed is everyone who does not continue to do everything written in the Book of the Law.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29113R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29113R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Clearly no one who relies on the law is justified before God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29114S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29114S\"></sup> because “the righteous will live by faith.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29114T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29114T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The law is not based on faith; on the contrary, it says, “The person who does these things will live by them.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29115U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29115U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Christ redeemed us from the curse of the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29116V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29116V\"></sup> by becoming a curse for us, for it is written: “Cursed is everyone who is hung on a pole.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29116W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29116W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He redeemed us in order that the blessing given to Abraham might come to the Gentiles through Christ Jesus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29117X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29117X\"></sup> so that by faith we might receive the promise of the Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29117Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29117Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Brothers and sisters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29118Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29118Z\"></sup> let me take an example from everyday life. Just as no one can set aside or add to a human covenant that has been duly established, so it is in this case.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The promises were spoken to Abraham and to his seed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29119AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29119AA\"></sup> Scripture does not say “and to seeds,” meaning many people, but “and to your seed,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29119AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29119AB\"></sup> meaning one person, who is Christ.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>What I mean is this: The law, introduced 430 years<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29120AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29120AC\"></sup> later, does not set aside the covenant previously established by God and thus do away with the promise.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For if the inheritance depends on the law, then it no longer depends on the promise;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29121AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29121AD\"></sup> but God in his grace gave it to Abraham through a promise.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Why, then, was the law given at all? It was added because of transgressions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29122AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29122AE\"></sup> until the Seed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29122AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29122AF\"></sup> to whom the promise referred had come. The law was given through angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29122AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29122AG\"></sup> and entrusted to a mediator.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29122AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29122AH\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>A mediator,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29123AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29123AI\"></sup> however, implies more than one party; but God is one.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Is the law, therefore, opposed to the promises of God? Absolutely not!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29124AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29124AJ\"></sup> For if a law had been given that could impart life, then righteousness would certainly have come by the law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29124AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29124AK\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But Scripture has locked up everything under the control of sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29125AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29125AL\"></sup> so that what was promised, being given through faith in Jesus Christ, might be given to those who believe.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Before the coming of this faith, we were held in custody<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29126AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29126AM\"></sup> under the law, locked up until the faith that was to come would be revealed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29126AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29126AN\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So the law was our guardian until Christ came<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29127AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29127AO\"></sup> that we might be justified by faith.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29127AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29127AP\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now that this faith has come, we are no longer under a guardian.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29128AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29128AQ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>So in Christ Jesus you are all children of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29129AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29129AR\"></sup> through faith,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>for all of you who were baptized into Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29130AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29130AS\"></sup> have clothed yourselves with Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29130AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29130AT\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>There is neither Jew nor Gentile, neither slave nor free,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29131AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29131AU\"></sup> nor is there male and female,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29131AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29131AV\"></sup> for you are all one in Christ Jesus.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29131AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29131AW\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>If you belong to Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29132AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29132AX\"></sup> then you are Abraham’s seed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29132AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29132AY\"></sup> and heirs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29132AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29132AZ\"></sup> according to the promise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29132BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29132BA\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>What I am saying is that as long as an heir is underage, he is no different from a slave, although he owns the whole estate.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The heir is subject to guardians and trustees until the time set by his father.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So also, when we were underage, we were in slavery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29135A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29135A\"></sup> under the elemental spiritual forces of the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29135B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29135B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But when the set time had fully come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29136C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29136C\"></sup> God sent his Son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29136D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29136D\"></sup> born of a woman,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29136E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29136E\"></sup> born under the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29136F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29136F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>to redeem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29137G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29137G\"></sup> those under the law, that we might receive adoption<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29137H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29137H\"></sup> to sonship.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29137I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29137I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Because you are his sons, God sent the Spirit of his Son<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29138J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29138J\"></sup> into our hearts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29138K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29138K\"></sup> the Spirit who calls out, <i>“Abba</i>, Father.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29138L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29138L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So you are no longer a slave, but God’s child; and since you are his child, God has made you also an heir.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29139M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29139M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Formerly, when you did not know God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29140N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29140N\"></sup> you were slaves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29140O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29140O\"></sup> to those who by nature are not gods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29140P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29140P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But now that you know God—or rather are known by God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29141Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29141Q\"></sup>—how is it that you are turning back to those weak and miserable forces? Do you wish to be enslaved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29141R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29141R\"></sup> by them all over again?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29141S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29141S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You are observing special days and months and seasons and years!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29142T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29142T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I fear for you, that somehow I have wasted my efforts on you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29143U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29143U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I plead with you, brothers and sisters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29144V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29144V\"></sup> become like me, for I became like you. You did me no wrong.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>As you know, it was because of an illness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29145W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29145W\"></sup> that I first preached the gospel to you,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and even though my illness was a trial to you, you did not treat me with contempt or scorn. Instead, you welcomed me as if I were an angel of God, as if I were Christ Jesus himself.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29146X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29146X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Where, then, is your blessing of me now? I can testify that, if you could have done so, you would have torn out your eyes and given them to me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Have I now become your enemy by telling you the truth?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29148Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29148Y\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Those people are zealous to win you over, but for no good. What they want is to alienate you from us, so that you may have zeal for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29149Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29149Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>It is fine to be zealous, provided the purpose is good, and to be so always, not just when I am with you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29150AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29150AA\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>My dear children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29151AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29151AB\"></sup> for whom I am again in the pains of childbirth until Christ is formed in you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29151AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29151AC\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>how I wish I could be with you now and change my tone, because I am perplexed about you!",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Tell me, you who want to be under the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29153AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29153AD\"></sup> are you not aware of what the law says?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For it is written that Abraham had two sons, one by the slave woman<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29154AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29154AE\"></sup> and the other by the free woman.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29154AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29154AF\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>His son by the slave woman was born according to the flesh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29155AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29155AG\"></sup> but his son by the free woman was born as the result of a divine promise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29155AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29155AH\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>These things are being taken figuratively: The women represent two covenants. One covenant is from Mount Sinai and bears children who are to be slaves: This is Hagar.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now Hagar stands for Mount Sinai in Arabia and corresponds to the present city of Jerusalem, because she is in slavery with her children.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But the Jerusalem that is above<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29158AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29158AI\"></sup> is free, and she is our mother.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For it is written:“Be glad, barren woman,you who never bore a child;shout for joy and cry aloud,you who were never in labor;because more are the children of the desolate womanthan of her who has a husband.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29159AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29159AJ\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Now you, brothers and sisters, like Isaac, are children of promise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29160AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29160AK\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>At that time the son born according to the flesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29161AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29161AL\"></sup> persecuted the son born by the power of the Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29161AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29161AM\"></sup> It is the same now.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But what does Scripture say? “Get rid of the slave woman and her son, for the slave woman’s son will never share in the inheritance with the free woman’s son.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29162AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29162AN\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Therefore, brothers and sisters, we are not children of the slave woman,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29163AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29163AO\"></sup> but of the free woman.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29163AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29163AP\"></sup>"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>It is for freedom that Christ has set us free.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29164A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29164A\"></sup> Stand firm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29164B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29164B\"></sup> then, and do not let yourselves be burdened again by a yoke of slavery.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29164C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29164C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Mark my words! I, Paul, tell you that if you let yourselves be circumcised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29165D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29165D\"></sup> Christ will be of no value to you at all.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Again I declare to every man who lets himself be circumcised that he is obligated to obey the whole law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29166E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29166E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You who are trying to be justified by the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29167F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29167F\"></sup> have been alienated from Christ; you have fallen away from grace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29167G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29167G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For through the Spirit we eagerly await by faith the righteousness for which we hope.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29168H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29168H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For in Christ Jesus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29169I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29169I\"></sup> neither circumcision nor uncircumcision has any value.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29169J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29169J\"></sup> The only thing that counts is faith expressing itself through love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29169K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29169K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You were running a good race.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29170L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29170L\"></sup> Who cut in on you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29170M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29170M\"></sup> to keep you from obeying the truth?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>That kind of persuasion does not come from the one who calls you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29171N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29171N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“A little yeast works through the whole batch of dough.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29172O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29172O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I am confident<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29173P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29173P\"></sup> in the Lord that you will take no other view.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29173Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29173Q\"></sup> The one who is throwing you into confusion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29173R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29173R\"></sup> whoever that may be, will have to pay the penalty.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Brothers and sisters, if I am still preaching circumcision, why am I still being persecuted?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29174S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29174S\"></sup> In that case the offense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29174T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29174T\"></sup> of the cross has been abolished.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>As for those agitators,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29175U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29175U\"></sup> I wish they would go the whole way and emasculate themselves!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You, my brothers and sisters, were called to be free.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29176V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29176V\"></sup> But do not use your freedom to indulge the flesh;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29176W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29176W\"></sup> rather, serve one another<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29176X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29176X\"></sup> humbly in love.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the entire law is fulfilled in keeping this one command: “Love your neighbor as yourself.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29177Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29177Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If you bite and devour each other, watch out or you will be destroyed by each other.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So I say, walk by the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29179Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29179Z\"></sup> and you will not gratify the desires of the flesh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29179AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29179AA\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For the flesh desires what is contrary to the Spirit, and the Spirit what is contrary to the flesh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29180AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29180AB\"></sup> They are in conflict with each other, so that you are not to do whatever you want.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29180AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29180AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But if you are led by the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29181AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29181AD\"></sup> you are not under the law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29181AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29181AE\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The acts of the flesh are obvious: sexual immorality,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29182AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29182AF\"></sup> impurity and debauchery;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>idolatry and witchcraft; hatred, discord, jealousy, fits of rage, selfish ambition, dissensions, factions",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and envy; drunkenness, orgies, and the like.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29184AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29184AG\"></sup> I warn you, as I did before, that those who live like this will not inherit the kingdom of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29184AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29184AH\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But the fruit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29185AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29185AI\"></sup> of the Spirit is love,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29185AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29185AJ\"></sup> joy, peace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29185AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29185AK\"></sup> forbearance, kindness, goodness, faithfulness,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>gentleness and self-control.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29186AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29186AL\"></sup> Against such things there is no law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29186AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29186AM\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Those who belong to Christ Jesus have crucified the flesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29187AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29187AN\"></sup> with its passions and desires.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29187AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29187AO\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Since we live by the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29188AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29188AP\"></sup> let us keep in step with the Spirit.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Let us not become conceited,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29189AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29189AQ\"></sup> provoking and envying each other."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Brothers and sisters, if someone is caught in a sin, you who live by the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29190A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29190A\"></sup> should restore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29190B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29190B\"></sup> that person gently. But watch yourselves, or you also may be tempted.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Carry each other’s burdens, and in this way you will fulfill the law of Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29191C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29191C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If anyone thinks they are something<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29192D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29192D\"></sup> when they are not, they deceive themselves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29192E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29192E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Each one should test their own actions. Then they can take pride in themselves alone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29193F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29193F\"></sup> without comparing themselves to someone else,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29193G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29193G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for each one should carry their own load.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29194H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29194H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Nevertheless, the one who receives instruction in the word should share all good things with their instructor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29195I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29195I\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Do not be deceived:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29196J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29196J\"></sup> God cannot be mocked. A man reaps what he sows.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29196K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29196K\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Whoever sows to please their flesh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29197L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29197L\"></sup> from the flesh will reap destruction;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29197M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29197M\"></sup> whoever sows to please the Spirit, from the Spirit will reap eternal life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29197N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29197N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Let us not become weary in doing good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29198O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29198O\"></sup> for at the proper time we will reap a harvest if we do not give up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29198P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29198P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Therefore, as we have opportunity, let us do good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29199Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29199Q\"></sup> to all people, especially to those who belong to the family<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29199R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29199R\"></sup> of believers.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>See what large letters I use as I write to you with my own hand!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29200S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29200S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Those who want to impress people by means of the flesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29201T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29201T\"></sup> are trying to compel you to be circumcised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29201U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29201U\"></sup> The only reason they do this is to avoid being persecuted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29201V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29201V\"></sup> for the cross of Christ.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Not even those who are circumcised keep the law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29202W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29202W\"></sup> yet they want you to be circumcised that they may boast about your circumcision in the flesh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29202X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29202X\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>May I never boast except in the cross of our Lord Jesus Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29203Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29203Y\"></sup> through which the world has been crucified to me, and I to the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29203Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29203Z\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Neither circumcision nor uncircumcision means anything;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29204AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29204AA\"></sup> what counts is the new creation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29204AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29204AB\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Peace and mercy to all who follow this rule—to the Israel of God.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>From now on, let no one cause me trouble, for I bear on my body the marks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29206AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29206AC\"></sup> of Jesus.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29207AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29207AD\"></sup> be with your spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29207AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29207AE\"></sup> brothers and sisters. Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;